channel.description:
I know. I know I haven’t posted in a while... I just feel, left behind y’know? Ever since I lost my subscription, I just haven’t been able to create music as good as something like ᵛᴱᴿᵀᴵᴳᴼ, but I’ve still been trying (well, somewhat) and I’ll still try, because even if I take a very long break, I would never, in many lifetimes use something other than Auxy and GarageBand (although rarely). Sorry for digressing, but here’s the track!
https://soundcloud.com/dubbtrasx/plains
Stay...happy, because I won’t if you won’t.
